  nodes:
  - id: start
    speakerID: owner
    text: "Ah, you must be Lyra Durand. Finally. I was starting to think all those
      stories about \u201Cthe medium of Paris\u201D were just marketing nonsense."
    nextNodeID: 1
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags:
    - {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8026d71d73230a548b720e9ed6b330cf, type: 2}
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
    expression: 0
  - id: 1
    speakerID: lyra
    text: "Lyra Durand. And yes, I can see them. You\u2019re Ren\xE9 Venue, I assume?"
    nextNodeID: 2
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
    expression: 1
  - id: 2
    speakerID: owner
    text: "Good. Then maybe you can help me before this place loses all its customers.
      Strange humming in the halls, paintings moving on their own\u2026 and all this
      right before Vivienne Encore\u2019s fiftieth death anniversary."
    nextNodeID: 3
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
    expression: 5
  - id: 3
    speakerID: lyra
    text: Vivienne Encore. The opera singer
    nextNodeID: 4
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
    expression: 5
  - id: 4
    speakerID: owner
    text: The Vivienne Encore. People come from everywhere to see this mansion because
      of her story. Or they did, before the ghost started terrorizing everyone.
    nextNodeID: 5
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 1
    expression: 0
  - id: 5
    speakerID: lyra
    text: "Spirits don\u2019t usually become violent without a reason."
    nextNodeID: 6
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
    expression: 5
  - id: 6
    speakerID: owner
    text: "Well, whatever the reason is, it\u2019s costing me money. Last night a
      chandelier nearly crushed two tourists."
    nextNodeID: 7
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
    expression: 5
  - id: 7
    speakerID: lyra
    text: When did the disturbances begin?
    nextNodeID: 8
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
    expression: 5
  - id: 8
    speakerID: owner
    text: "A few weeks ago. First the singing started at night. Then objects began
      moving, mirrors shattered\u2026 some staff even claimed they saw Vivienne herself
      wandering the upper floor."
    nextNodeID: 9
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
    expression: 3
  - id: 9
    speakerID: lyra
    text: And what do you know about her death?
    nextNodeID: 10
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
    expression: 5
  - id: 10
    speakerID: owner
    text: "Officially? A tragic accident. But people whispered about jealousy, inheritance
      fights\u2026 even betrayal from those close to her."
    nextNodeID: 11
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
    expression: 5
  - id: 11
    speakerID: lyra
    text: Close to her how?
    nextNodeID: 12
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
    expression: 5
  - id: 12
    speakerID: owner
    text: "A former lover, rivals, a few servants\u2026 I don\u2019t know the details.
      I just bought the mansion years later."
    nextNodeID: 13
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
    expression: 3
  - id: 13
    speakerID: lyra
    text: And her remains?
    nextNodeID: 14
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
    expression: 5
  - id: 14
    speakerID: owner
    text: Most of Vivienne and her family were moved to the catacombs long ago. Stored
      there with countless others.
    nextNodeID: 
    choices:
    - text: "I see\u2026 Then that\u2019s probably where this all began."
      nextNodeID: 
